<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal Profile</title>
</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Ewang Gilles Paques</h1>
        <p>Welcome to my personal profile page.</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>
                I am a beginner web developer learning HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
                I enjoy building websites and improving my programming skills.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>My Interests</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Web Development</li>
                <li>Programming</li>
                <li>Technology</li>
                <li>Learning new skills</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>My GitHub</h2>
            <p>
                You can view my projects here:
                <a href="https://github.com/paquesjunior55-source" target="_blank">
                    Visit my GitHub
                </a>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>My Picture</h2>
            <img src="profile.jpg" alt="My profile picture">
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>©️ 2026 Ewang Gilles Paques</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
